dict.string: Finally, the Sodor Search and Rescue Centre and the Misty Island Tunnel were officially opened! “Today is a very special day, made possible by very special engines,” The Fat Controller said. The people cheered and the engines peeped. Thomas, surrounded by his old and new friends, beamed with pride.
